		"description": "<p>At 6th level your ability to use your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.0rAgcjGN39v9X9v7]{Mind Strike} grows intensely and is combined with your telekinetic prowess. You can unleash a wave of power so intense it blasts your enemies back. As an action you expend your psychic focus to create a line of force 15ft wide and 60ft long using a chosen mind strike. All creatures within the area must make a Dexterity save, for ballistic or thymokinetic psionic tornadoes, or a Wisdom save, for telekinetic and telepathic psionic tornadoes. On a failure they take damage appropriate to your chosen mind strike and are thrown up to 15ft away from your line’s area. On a successful saving throw they take half damage and are pushed out of the line’s area to the nearest safe square. You may apply only the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.u4k9gzSY5gGIvR1P]{Boggle Mind} or @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.nBIzzpnTeZ2SWGQb]{Psionic Blast} attack modes to this special mind strike.</p>",
